Title: Summer Walker - "Karma" (Live) | Vevo DSCVR
Description:
Summer Walker ‚Äì ‚ÄúKarma‚Äù Live Performance | Vevo
 
Summer Walker needs love. She sings all about it in her aptly titled, ‚ÄúGirls Need Love.‚Äù But while her song lyrics sizzle with sex appeal, the Atlanta newcomer‚Äôs artistry is also in need of affection. Her 2018 debut, ‚ÄòLast Days of Summer,‚Äô brims with old school heartache and millennial panache. That combination, combined with Walker‚Äôs swagger and forthright personality, just might help her capture 2019‚Äôs It Girl crown. Recently, Vevo connected with her for cool performances of ‚ÄúGirls Need Love‚Äù and ‚ÄúKarma‚Äù from the ‚ÄòLast Days‚Äô album. The former got a boost this year by way of a Drake verse for the remix. Add that material to her new EP, ‚ÄòClear,‚Äô and your cold winter nights will feel a bit warmer.
